Comment: 0,0:00:00.02,0:00:00.06,chapters,,0,0,0,,Intro
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.50,0:00:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooishi-san
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.63,0:00:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Because inbound recovery is expected, I have set up the Japanese content
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.43,0:00:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you please take a look?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.58,0:00:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll take a look
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.10,0:00:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.28,0:00:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you you make the name of the star bigger?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.62,0:00:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, how is the media coverage for tomorrow's supplement company launch going to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.46,0:00:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday's special show about Ichiro teaching baseball to kids was great
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.03,0:00:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Summer equals Koushien after all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.74,0:00:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweat, mud and tears melts together under the summer sun, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.63,0:00:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.32,0:00:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But Chief, playing sports under
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.49,0:00:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,the blazing hot sun is kind of outdated don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.28,0:00:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Just the other day it was 30 degrees in the middle of the night
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.13,0:00:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that my phone was broken
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.44,0:01:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Singing the school anthem to support their school at the Alps stand
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.92,0:01:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's youth for you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.87,0:01:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's summer in Japan for you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.32,0:01:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so too, Kirimura-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.84,0:01:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it global warming? Or is it the pole shift?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.34,0:01:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember my school anthem
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.63,0:01:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think that it's absurd that the temperature setting for air conditioning the whole building is the same for all floors?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.25,0:01:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It depends on the season, only during summers and winters
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.68,0:01:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Your generation also watches Koushien, right Komukai?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.20,0:01:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see kids keep looking at the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.27,0:01:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.27,0:01:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's certainly a bit chilly over here
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.19,0:01:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to file a complaint?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.94,0:01:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You watch Koushien, right Komukai?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.69,0:01:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,At least reply when people are talking to you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.76,0:01:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this also a power harassment, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.96,0:01:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.15,0:01:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.54,0:01:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.03,0:01:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.68,0:01:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It sure is peaceful over here
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.20,0:01:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.68,0:01:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So precious
Comment: 0,0:01:53.21,0:01:53.25,chapters,,0,0,0,,OP
Comment: 0,0:02:52.77,0:02:52.82,chapters,,0,0,0,,Part A
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.28,0:02:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, it's time
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.78,0:02:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.00,0:03:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,As you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.64,0:03:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,due to the wave of digitalization
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.21,0:03:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,the event industry is in transition
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.35,0:03:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I want everyone to respond accordingly just like Ooishi-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.17,0:03:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you, Ooishi-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.72,0:03:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do my best
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.01,0:03:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.11,0:03:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooishi-san is good looking, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.06,0:03:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not interested in him at all
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.19,0:03:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooishi-kun sure is getting fat
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.86,0:03:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like Inuzuka-kun in his younger days
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.59,0:03:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just greasy back then
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.48,0:03:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,They should have done this award ceremony over Zoom
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.01,0:03:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just the best Ooishi-san
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.24,0:03:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There's an interesting freshman in department 1
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.92,0:03:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody is getting assigned to be under me in department 3, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.15,0:03:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Next up is the joint project presentation
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.25,0:03:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Department 1 proposes an IoT project in depopulated areas
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.25,0:03:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a medium-to-long-term city development project
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.84,0:03:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We will strive for regional revitalization through IoT
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.22,0:03:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Department 2 proposes
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.93,0:04:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,a metaverse avatar fashion show
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.89,0:04:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,A famous person's avatar will appear on the show,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.56,0:04:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,so you can enjoy an exclusive experience
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.72,0:04:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,In the metaverse that is all the rage these days...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.85,0:04:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What department 3 came up with is
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.15,0:04:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,a cat park where you can interact with cats
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.78,0:04:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We will prepare a number of attractions while they are playing the the cute cats
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.14,0:04:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Komukai
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.41,0:04:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.47,0:04:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting hot water
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.20,0:04:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what I'm asking you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.98,0:04:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The joint presentation, what was that all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.01,0:04:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The cat park?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.38,0:04:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that a joke?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.26,0:04:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Or are you guys for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.03,0:04:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We came up with a project, it's all good
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.04,0:04:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think that it's not good to just come up with something to clear your quota?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.32,0:04:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.36,0:04:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Think about moving people and money in your head
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.88,0:04:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to give it all that you got
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.12,0:04:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Work using your own name
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.84,0:04:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay with just by getting your paycheck?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.43,0:04:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I did something to you, Asai?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.95,0:04:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You said during the entrance ceremony to do our best because we don't have that many people that enter the company at the same time
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.94,0:04:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I did?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.15,0:04:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm tired watching department 3
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.98,0:04:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.73,0:04:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you eavesdropping, Nakano-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.25,0:04:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I just overheard on my way to get some coffee
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.82,0:04:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Department 3 is the only one in red
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.35,0:04:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So unpleasant
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.40,0:05:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Your project is interesting, but I just can't see it actually happening
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.64,0:05:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you evaluated your own project?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.66,0:05:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If you take what others have told you and then you tell other people as is, I'm going to punch you{TODO: what does this mean}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.70,0:05:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay to be passionate, but do it yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.23,0:05:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Komukai
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.50,0:05:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you looking at your phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.06,0:05:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's lunch
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.42,0:05:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.88,0:05:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Since when you become a mass production-type person?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.88,0:05:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Mass production-type?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.30,0:05:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Working under the radar, avoiding conflicts,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.26,0:05:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,getting your paycheck,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.39,0:05:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,looking forward to lunch all the time
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.66,0:05:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and then posting said lunch on a SNS site that nobody sees
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.91,0:05:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's out of line
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.47,0:05:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You know just how hard the event industry is, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.39,0:05:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The way things are going, there's a rumor that department 3 is getting disbanded
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.00,0:05:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.58,0:05:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that everything would be fine if I'm here, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.87,0:05:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,An organization spreads those kinds of rumors from time to time...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.17,0:05:57.67,Signs,,0,0,0,,Mass production-type
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.30,0:06:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,They might ask me to retire early
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.69,0:06:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I'll move somewhere when the time comes
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.88,0:06:05.55,Signs,,0,0,0,,Background character{mob chara}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.55,0:06:07.26,Signs,,0,0,0,,NPC{small-fry chara}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.54,0:06:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to stay here forever, because it's peaceful
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.12,0:06:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Kijimura-san
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.39,0:06:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We still don't know what the future holds
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.14,0:06:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.94,0:06:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do everything that we can for our client
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.22,0:06:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Manten Nodoame's event
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.30,0:06:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't this be a DM instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.04,0:06:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's our love for Manten Nodoame
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.74,0:06:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.50,0:06:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Our thoughts and feelings will reach them
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.30,0:06:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up with that friend of yours, Asai?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.38,0:06:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that he has a strong desire for approval
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.02,0:06:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Agreed
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.64,0:06:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Nakano-san
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.46,0:06:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.58,0:06:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I a mass production-type person?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.29,0:06:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What makes you happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.40,0:06:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,When I chill out at home
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.24,0:06:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.68,0:06:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's fun
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.14,0:06:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want to be in the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.86,0:06:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The future...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.10,0:06:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you, Nakano-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.02,0:06:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be rich
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.19,0:07:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,As expected from you
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.14,0:07:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to maintain the status quo as much as possible
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.14,0:07:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there something that you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.22,0:07:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A good hair dryer
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.31,0:07:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Club activities?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.13,0:07:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I was in the dance club during middle school
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.38,0:07:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,and I didn't join any clubs in high school
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.45,0:07:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You like to dance?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.50,0:07:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone was doing it at the time
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.51,0:07:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What about college?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.18,0:07:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Literature department, majoring in German literature
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.46,0:07:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What attracted you to German literature?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.84,0:07:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the easiest department to get into
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.60,0:07:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me your war story
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.32,0:07:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I never missed a day of cram school
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.71,0:07:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the election?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.38,0:07:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have an interest, but I do vote
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.77,0:07:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Where do you buy your clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.03,0:07:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I bought them all at the train station
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.46,0:07:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.56,0:07:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a mass production-type person
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.94,0:07:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I see
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.51,0:07:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,A mass production-type Riko with no peaks nor valleys
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.90,0:07:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's even worse that what Asai said to me
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.88,0:07:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.47,0:07:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't stop working
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.91,0:07:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.24,0:07:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, can I do my own work now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.98,0:07:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The one from the second division, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.22,0:07:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, please help her
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.00,0:07:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.81,0:07:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,A rare store festival
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.76,0:07:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.91,0:07:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You know that there used to be a lot of independent stores like electric, stationary and candy stores in town,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.42,0:07:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,but they're all now few and far between, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.17,0:07:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This project aims to show off the uniqueness of such retro spaces
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.78,0:08:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeing the trophies at the hardware store gets my blood pumping
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.37,0:08:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,For me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.38,0:08:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I loved the toy store
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.14,0:08:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt like everything in that store was waiting for me
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.01,0:08:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,My heart was racing every time I passed it
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.60,0:08:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything was sparkling
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.62,0:08:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I was interested in things like robots, plastic models, or dinosaurs
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.90,0:08:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But I was nervous every time I passed it for some reason
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.94,0:08:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I was excited looking at dolls or transforming sticks
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.04,0:08:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,A mass production-type where she has lost her dreams, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.33,0:08:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't say that
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.50,0:08:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Just kidding
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.78,0:08:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, if you see such a store, go take a look, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.40,0:08:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.10,0:08:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.90,0:08:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Since when you become a mass production-type person?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.74,0:08:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.74,0:08:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.26,0:08:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.47,0:08:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Komukai
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.75,0:08:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.82,0:08:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you making a fool of yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.31,0:08:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.24,0:09:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you excited?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.50,0:09:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Is excitement necessary for adults?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.54,0:09:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard what he said to you earlier
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.91,0:09:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anything that you can get lost in?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.66,0:09:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Playing Pokemon or watching videos
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.23,0:09:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you like that so much that it makes your nose bleed?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.91,0:09:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.49,0:09:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You should go wild, so much so that it will make your nose bleed
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.14,0:09:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.17,0:09:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Go wild
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.42,0:09:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.47,0:09:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Go wild?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.66,0:09:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What did he mean by "go wild"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.36,0:09:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What is a mass production-type?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.75,0:09:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Toy store
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.95,0:09:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know there was a toy store here
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.87,0:09:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Model store?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.07,0:10:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Last shooting
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.24,0:11:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be surprised, I'm terribly sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.97,0:11:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.74,0:11:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,How many times have I told you to turn on the lights once it gets dark, Yassan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.04,0:11:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.56,0:11:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not here because I'm looking for something
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.28,0:11:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you like plastic models?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.61,0:11:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never built one before
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.87,0:11:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your first time, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.71,0:11:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I just entered this store on a whim
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.43,0:11:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,On a whim...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.03,0:11:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.23,0:11:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take your time and choose a plastic model
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.20,0:11:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You have plenty of time
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.15,0:11:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.41,0:11:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Mass production-type
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.84,0:12:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a mobile suit from the anime Mobile Suit Gundam that's used by the enemy force, the Zeon army:
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.06,0:12:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Main mass production-type Zaku
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.44,0:12:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Zaku
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.68,0:12:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You know Gundam, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.17,0:12:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Only the name
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.92,0:12:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Because Zaku is a mass production-type, it has no discerning trait and people say that it's a background character
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.74,0:12:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only for combat, but it is also used for security, large-scale construction and reconnaissance
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.50,0:12:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,In short, they serve as the foil to other distinct and strong mobile suits
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.69,0:12:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Foils...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.02,0:12:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But, one reason that Gundam is a long beloved series
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.32,0:12:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of these type of mass production-type appeared on screen
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.88,0:12:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So the production gives a sense of reality that there are ordinary soldiers that fought in wars
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.32,0:12:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,On top of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.24,0:12:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,For on land or for underwater use
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.01,0:12:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The charm of a mass production-type is that it has a lot of variations
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.71,0:12:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and because of that, people are still going crazy over it to this day
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.57,0:12:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The charm of a mass production-type...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.40,0:12:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.11,0:12:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to build it
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.38,0:12:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.58,0:12:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to build this over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.11,0:12:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.02,0:13:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's free of charge
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.12,0:13:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to pay for it
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.83,0:13:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's rare to see someone chose an old kit
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.32,0:13:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Old kit?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.52,0:13:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the start of everything
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.36,0:13:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the start of Gunplas
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.36,0:13:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What is your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.03,0:13:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Komukai Riko
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.66,0:13:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay then Riko-san
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.84,0:13:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Please go
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.93,0:13:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Go?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.52,0:13:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Riko!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.60,0:13:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.88,0:13:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko is off{TODO}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.15,0:13:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Open the box
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.01,0:13:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing that the parts are attached to is called a runner
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.92,0:13:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.28,0:13:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But it only has one color
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.24,0:13:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to paint it
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.78,0:13:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Paint?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.93,0:13:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get started
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.57,0:13:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You cut the part that connects the parts to the runner, they are called gates
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.56,0:13:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about the order this time
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.88,0:13:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,just start cutting wherever you want
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.11,0:14:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Released
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.14,0:14:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring it to life
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.77,0:14:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Carefully
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.88,0:14:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That is a 1/144 mass production-type Zaku
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.08,0:14:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That is an old type of plastic model called old kit
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.38,0:14:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,All the parts must be glued together
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.68,0:14:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The age range was changed from 8 years old and up to 15 years old and up
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.36,0:14:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a lot of information
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.33,0:14:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.36,0:14:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Next up is gluing the parts
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.07,0:15:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The newer models are snap fit and don't need any glue,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.49,0:15:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,but it is needed for old kits
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.85,0:15:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's glue for plastic models
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.79,0:15:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the first time using it
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.60,0:15:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I put too much glue on it
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.16,0:15:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, you can smooth it out later
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.41,0:15:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Smooth it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.19,0:15:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.89,0:16:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I broke it
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.27,0:16:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing that you can do about number 41
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.79,0:16:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Chiemi
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.35,0:16:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.74,0:16:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You continue building it, Riko
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.09,0:16:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No honorifics?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.02,0:16:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's done
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.30,0:16:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do next?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.39,0:16:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We wait until the glue is dry
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.96,0:16:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.92,0:16:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.92,0:16:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we're going to smooth out the excess glue
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.64,0:17:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to do the head
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.20,0:17:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's time to paint the Zaku
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.58,0:18:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Usually you paint it while looking at the box
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.72,0:18:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Failure is sometimes a gift
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.92,0:18:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You can fix it to your heart's content
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.09,0:18:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,To my heart's content...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.01,0:18:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do anything with plastic models
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.32,0:18:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no rule that says you have to paint it like the box
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.28,0:18:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Normally, you'd temporarily build it first before painting it to figure out the spots that is hard to paint over
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.64,0:19:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll teach you about that later
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.32,0:19:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The old kits...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.54,0:19:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Mass production-type Zaku
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.19,0:19:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Give birth!{TODO: is this a thing or can I change}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.44,0:19:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Give birth{TODO: ditto}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.20,0:19:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.16,0:19:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It felt like sound disappeared for a moment
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.87,0:19:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because of the amygdala that is located deep within your brain was working
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.28,0:20:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That part of the brain is usually tired because of information overload, but
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.22,0:20:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,When you can concentrate on just one thing, you feel energized and is able to concentrate
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.63,0:20:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You were in the zone
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.50,0:20:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I'm going to get a nose bleed
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.40,0:20:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.63,0:20:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So funny
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.02,0:20:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,They say that they can see the story just by looking at a masterpiece plastic model
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.48,0:20:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Mine is clunky so I don't see the story at all, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.56,0:20:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.89,0:20:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.35,0:20:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.78,0:20:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really cute
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.40,0:20:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Fondness is a form of love
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.84,0:20:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your very own mass production-type Zaku that you built yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.44,0:20:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,My very own mass production-type Zaku
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.48,0:20:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.11,0:20:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mention it
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.35,0:20:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Come again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.52,0:21:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen, Riko?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.07,0:21:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to deliver these documents
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.76,0:21:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm terribly sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.16,0:21:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You were too aggressive
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.64,0:21:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Think it over and don't worry about it
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.78,0:21:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Komukai-san
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.77,0:21:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.35,0:21:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,About the cat park that you presented during the joint presentation
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.04,0:21:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,There's not a lot of people who can pull it off
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.00,0:21:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.31,0:21:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.33,0:21:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like I was scolded, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.57,0:21:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think you were
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.60,0:21:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,department 3 might come to an end soon
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.88,0:21:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,A problematic person from department 1 is coming your way
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.26,0:22:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Asai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.83,0:22:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember what you told me the other day?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.43,0:22:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.80,0:22:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Komukai Riko, a mass production-type person
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.93,0:22:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.34,0:22:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying with a straight face...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.69,0:22:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.28,0:22:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Komukai...
